data.description: Move-in ready Three Bedroom Colonial, Updated full bath, two half baths, living room XL window, ceiling light, New Vinyl floor.  Large kitchen comes with newer refrigerator, gas stove, above range microwave, built-in dishwasher, ceiling light, oak cabinets, marble counter tops, Vinyl flooring. Dining room has Vinyl flooring, ceiling light. Pantry with window, ceiling light and tile floor.  Spacious family room comes with a door-wall to deck, carpet, window, ceiling light, large doorway to dining room and kitchen, half bath/laundry room combo, window, ceiling light, gas hookup for dryer, shelves, Vinyl floor.  Vinyl flooring on stairs to second floor, an hallway to linen closet, three bedrooms with new carpet.  First floor hallway has coat closet and Vinyl flooring.  Full basement has updated circuit box, 2nd laundry room with washer/dryer, forced air furnace with humidifier, Wifi thermostat, block windows and play room.  Exterior - fenced yard with gate, deck, 2.5 detached garage.Primary bedroom has a walk-in closet. New Roof on House and Garage, New Windows, New Vinyl Floor and Carpet.  Lamphere School District.  Elementary school is minutes away.  A Water Park, Nature Center, Golf Course all within walking distance.  An amazing family sub with lots of children.  Dead end street.  Possession at close.
